1.create project - ng new project-name

2.to run angular project - ng serve

3.to generate component - ng g c component-name


basic concepts 

1. Module : To import libraries ( Root Module- App Module )

2. Components : To generate ts,html,css, Root component-App component

3. Data Binding - sharing data within a component

    3.1 One way Binding - only single directional sharing

        3.1.1 component (ts file) to View (html page)

             3.1.1.1 String Interpolation - {{variable-name}}
             3.1.1.2 Property Binding - [tag attribute] = "class-property"

        3.1.2 View to Component
        
             3.1.2.1 Event Binding - [event name]= "function- call"
             3.1.2.1 Event Binding using $event - [event name]= "function- call ($event)"
